ikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1868}, {\"ngram\": \"world number\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1988}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2023 world championships\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has cleared heights over 4.8 metres on eight occasions in 2024 and became European bronze medallist in 4.73, though only managed third place with 4.65 at the London Diamond League meet in July.\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2197, \"end\": 2203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999993083293, \"rank\": 6.590859024469616e-10, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999999804459, \"rank\": 1.9341431096246316e-11, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"heights\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2058}, {\"ngram\": \"4.8 metres\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2074}, {\"ngram\": \"eight occasions\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2093}, {\"ngram\": \"European bronze medallist\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2138}, {\"ngram\": \"third place\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2179}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Caudery confessed: \\\"I am currently in a bit of shock.\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Caudery\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2277}, {\"ngram\": \"shock\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so disappointed.\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not have any excuse.\\\"\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any excuse\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her exit came not long after she had consoled team-mateHolly Bradshaw, who with bronze in Tokyo became the first Briton to win a pole vault medal, but ruled herself out in what she had already declared to be her final Games after she was unable to make 4.40.\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2399, \"end\": 2407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Layfield\", \"score\": 0.9999999102224177, \"rank\": 8.977563734865303e-08, \"text\": \"Bradshaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Layfield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Layfield\"}, {\"begin\": 2428, \"end\": 2433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999850627070047, \"rank\": 1.4937329040957763e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her exit\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"team\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2388}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2424}, {\"ngram\": \"the first Briton\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2457}, {\"ngram\": \"a pole vault medal\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"her final Games\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Caudery defended the decision to enter at 4.55, saying: \\\"4.55m is a bar that I jump day in, day out.\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2698, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Caudery\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2605}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2627}, {\"ngram\": \"4.55m\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2660}, {\"ngram\": \"a bar\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2669}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is not one piece of doubt in my mind that I wasn't going to clear it.\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2774, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one piece\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2721}, {\"ngram\": \"doubt\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2730}, {\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some people might say I came in too high, but that's certainly not mine or my coach's opinion.\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2871, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some people\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2788}, {\"ngram\": \"my coach's opinion\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I have been jumping 4.80 and 4.90 all year round, 4.55 should not have been a problem.\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2965, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is just a really unfortunate day.\\\"\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 3003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a really unfortunate day\", \"from\": 2972, \"to\": 3001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bradshaw was also devastated to miss out, in tears as she was consoled by Caudery on the track and emotional as she spoke to Eurosport after her fourth and final Olympics came to a close, and paid tribute to her late father.\", \"from\": 3005, \"to\": 3229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3005, \"end\": 3013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Layfield\", \"score\": 0.9999999102224177, \"rank\": 8.977563734865303e-08, \"text\": \"Bradshaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Layfield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Layfield\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 3050, \"to\": 3055}, {\"ngram\": \"Caudery\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3086}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3099}, {\"ngram\": \"Eurosport\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"her fourth and final Olympics\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3175}, {\"ngram\": \"tribute\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3209}, {\"ngram\": \"her late father\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"I am just crushed.\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3260, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew this was going to be my last champs.\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my last champs\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have only got a few competitions left, so I am heartbroken.\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3368, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few competitions\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been a really hard year and I wanted to come out and do myself proud and I really feel like I have not.\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really hard year\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is the first time I was pain-free all year, so I do not really know what happened.\", \"from\": 3479, \"to\": 3567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know it sounds daft, but the track and the environment and everything was too good and I was caught on the back foot, which is frustrating about pole vault.\", \"from\": 3568, \"to\": 3726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"daft\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3589}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 3595, \"to\": 3604}, {\"ngram\": \"the environment\", \"from\": 3609, \"to\": 3624}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3639}, {\"ngram\": \"the back foot\", \"from\": 3673, \"to\": 3686}, {\"ngram\": \"pole vault\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Mainly I just wanted to come out and do my dad proud.\", \"from\": 3728, \"to\": 3782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my dad\", \"from\": 3769, \"to\": 3775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You know, he passed away in November, and I really hope that I did that even though it did not go well.\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3886, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 3811, \"to\": 3819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The crowd really reminds me of London.\", \"from\": 3888, \"to\": 3927, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3920, \"end\": 3926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999993083293, \"rank\": 6.590859024469616e-10, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The crowd\", \"from\": 3889, \"to\": 3898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"it's kind of fitting that that was the start of my journey and this is the end.\", \"from\": 3928, \"to\": 4007, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 3963, \"to\": 3972}, {\"ngram\": \"my journey\", \"from\": 3976, \"to\": 3986}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 3999, \"to\": 4006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the first time I was pain-free all year, so I do not really know what happened \\\"You know, I really earned my place on this team.\", \"from\": 4009, \"to\": 4146, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 4017, \"to\": 4031}, {\"ngram\": \"my place\", \"from\": 4123, \"to\": 4131}, {\"ngram\": \"this team\", \"from\": 4135, \"to\": 4144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I fought really hard to get back and make it, and just to be here is a privilege and an honour and I am trying to soak it up.\", \"from\": 4147, \"to\": 4272, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a privilege\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4227}, {\"ngram\": \"an honour\", \"from\": 4232, \"to\": 4241}]}, {\"sen